==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cow tree
<hw>Cow" tree`</hw> <pr>(kou" tr?`)</pr>. <ety>[Cf. SP. <ets>palo de
vaca</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A tree (<spn>Galactodendron
utile</spn> or <spn>Brosimum Galactodendron</spn>) of South America,
which yields, on incision, a nourishing fluid, resembling
milk.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cowweed</ent>⟦br⟧
